creator: BANKOR
descriptionHtml:
NOTES! helps you to create & manage your notes/task :

1. Basic create, update, archive/done, delete note operation
2. Set reminder, add image, & add checkbox to your notes
3. Manage notes with label
4. Backup/Restore with Google Drive
5. Light & Dark Theme

It's still in BETA version, but there will be more features to come :D
descriptionShort: NOTES! helps you to create & manage your notes/task

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Add note color selector

Bug fixes & performance improvements
